instruction: Tell me which Disney character has the most iconic clothes.
output: The Disney character with the most iconic clothing is undoubtedly Minnie Mouse, who is best known for her signature red-and-white polka-dot dress. Her signature look is said to be based on the flapper style of the 1930s. Minnie's classic look is timeless and she has been wearing this iconic outfit since she made her debut in 1928.
